data.description: Lovely ranch style home seated in Northern Erath County, in the highly sought after Huckabay ISD. 4-bedroom, 3-bath home has recently been updated and offers a relaxing country feel. Open floor plan with a split bedroom layout and tons of natural lighting. Set up & ready for your family, your horses, farming, gardening or 4H projects. 4.31 acres that is fenced & cross fenced with pipe, five turn outs or traps and a larger grazing pasture in the back. Also located on the property is a 100x35 barn set up with 7-stalls, wash bay, separate feed and tack room, plus plenty of room for hay storage. Three entrances into the property with several circle drives making for easy trailer maneuvering and ample parking. Large back patio offers a great spot for summertime BBQs. Added bonuses include the two-bay attached carport and 2 large RV or trailer covered parking. Conveniently located across the street from the school. Ready for you to come make it yours and it won't last long!
